Name: Znkl - 177
About the game: Znkl - 177 is a simple physical puzzle. The player's goal is to deliver a capsule with information to the spaceship. You are a pilot of the spaceship 'Znkl - 177'. You need to deliver a capsule with important information to the cargo spaceship. - 2 shooting modes (1-10 two modes. 11-20 only LMB, 21-30 only RMB) - 30 levels - Pleasant music - Steam achievements Controls: LMB, RMB -Shot, R - Restart level, arrows - control Credits: This game was created using Clickteam Fusion 2.5! Music by Neocoda.
